As a beauty influencer and interior designer, Ronnie Woods examines the intersection of objectification and embodied consciousness through a lens of dummy advocacy. She has appeared on NBC, Subway Takes with Kareem Rahma, and in The New York Times Style Section. Fresh from her European tour, Ronnie is now turning inward and penning her memoir, The Dummy in Me. Ronnie is excited to be making her New Theater Hollywood debut. <br/>
